### 新建订单
PUT http://{{host}}{{baseUrl}}/order
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 2,
  "amount": 12.34
}

### 删除订单
DELETE http://{{host}}{{baseUrl}}order
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": 1
}

### 更新订单
POST http://{{host}}{{baseUrl}}order
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": 2,
  "userId": 2,
  "amount": 12.345
}

### 查询订单
GET http://{{host}}{{baseUrl}}order?id=2
Content-Type: application/json


### 列表查询订单
GET http://{{host}}{{baseUrl}}order/list?page=1&size=20
Content-Type: application/json

